title: Man Kneeling Medium Skin Tone
description: A man is depicted kneeling on one knee, with a medium skin tone. This emoji often signifies prayer, respect, apology, or a proposal.
apple_vendor_description: The man kneeling emoji on Apple devices showcases a figure in a thoughtful pose, with one knee gently bent and resting on the ground, embodying contemplation or reverence. Apple's signature smooth gradients and realistic lighting create a sense of depth and naturalism in the figure's posture and medium skin tone. This emoji on Apple devices can convey humility, prayer, or a moment of quiet reflection.
